  "text": "A category of dental composite with a resin matrix, based on ring-opening monomers, has been introduced to the market. This hydrophobic composite drives from the combination of siloxane and oxirane, thus given the name silorane. The major advantage of this restorative material is its reduced volumetric shrinkage [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
